<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="14" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="14.[93,620,210,702]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">
COMMENTS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Hartert" box="[274,500,212,234]" firstAuthor="Hartert" page="14" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" pagination="4 - 63" refId="ref125652" refString="Hartert, E. 1918 a. Types of birds in the Tring Museum. A. Types in the Brehm Collection. Novitates Zoologicae 25: 4 - 63." type="journal article" year="1918" yearSuffix="a">Hartert (1918a: 14)</bibRefCitation>
, by listing the male collected on 
<date box="[361,584,242,264]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" value="1826-12-10">10 December 1826</date>
as the type, designated it the 
<typeStatus box="[469,574,271,293]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[93,191,301,322]" class="Aves" family="Passeridae" genus="Petronia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="saxorum">
<emphasis box="[93,191,301,322]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">saxorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It is tied together with a female, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[93,279,329,350]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">AMNH 456564</emphasis>
, collected on 
<date pageId="14" pageNumber="14" value="1826-12-10">10 December 1826</date>
, a 
<typeStatus box="[192,353,358,380]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">paralectotype</typeStatus>
, also labeled 
<taxonomicName box="[521,619,359,380]" class="Aves" family="Passeridae" genus="Petronia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="saxorum">
<emphasis box="[521,619,359,380]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">saxorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Brehm. There are two additional 
<typeStatus pageId="14" pageNumber="14">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
in AMNH labeled 
<taxonomicName box="[475,573,417,438]" class="Aves" family="Passeridae" genus="Petronia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="saxorum">
<emphasis box="[475,573,417,438]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">saxorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Brehm: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[187,369,446,467]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">AMNH 456566</emphasis>
, female juvenile, and 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[93,273,475,496]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">AMNH 456567</emphasis>
, male juvenile, both collected at Lobeda near Jena, on 
<date box="[391,579,504,526]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" value="1826-08-10">10 August 1826</date>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[93,620,210,702]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">
Four additional Brehm specimens cataloged as 
<taxonomicName authority="petronia petronia" authorityName="petronia petronia (Linnaeus" authorityYear="1766" box="[198,500,564,585]" class="Aves" family="Passeridae" genus="Petronia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="petronia" subSpecies="petronia">
<emphasis box="[198,500,564,585]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">Petronia petronia petronia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and from Lobeda were exchanged with ZFMK. They may be 
<typeStatus box="[209,377,622,644]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
of 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">
<taxonomicName box="[440,615,621,644]" class="Aves" family="Passeridae" genus="Petronia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macrorhynchos">macrorhynchos</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[93,190,652,673]" class="Aves" family="Aves (awaiting allocation)" genus="Pyrgita" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aves (awaiting allocation)" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="rupestris">rupestris</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
, or 
<taxonomicName box="[259,357,652,673]" class="Aves" family="Passeridae" genus="Petronia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="saxorum">
<emphasis box="[259,357,652,673]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">saxorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, depending on how Brehm had labeled them.
</paragraph>
